  "description": "This operation performs purchase refund. A refund of a purchase contains the following actions:\n- Calling the charging interface refund method.\n- Update purchase and set it to be refunded.\n- Write a post to a file with date, premiumResourceType, purchaseId, serviceId, partnerId",
